    dc:creator "Monteiro, Cassandra Moraes; Brasil-Sato, Marilia Carvalho" ;
    dc:date "2014" ;
    dc:title "A new species of Anacanthoroides and redescription of Apedunculata discoidea (Monogenoidea) parasitizing Prochilodus argenteus (Actinopterygii) from the São Francisco River, Brazil" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.230265> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.230265>
    dc:description "FIGURES 1 – 4. Anacanthoroides sanctifrancisci n. sp. from ‘ curimatã-pacú’, Prochilodus argenteus from the São Francisco River, Brazil, in ventral view. (1) Whole mount (composite). (2) Copulatory complex. (3) Hook. (4) Reduced hook. Scale = 150 µm (1) and 15 µm (2 – 4)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/230265/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

